The evidence with the title 'Judging Reagan's legacy: the Gipper meets the truth-o-meter ... ' says Feb 8, 2011  ... Former Arkansas Republican gov. Mike Huckabee : "(Ronald Reagan) raised taxes a billion dollars in his first year as governor of California." In the summer of 1967, during Reagan's first year as governor and contrary to his campaign promises, Reagan signed a record tax increase for the state of California  ... 
